ng Brightside again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Manza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlUdzP9o1L8qTWipbTcdjW3aAT4CspX-o8gj8Kwwb3Voi75n4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have had an excellent experience with Jonathan and Brightside! We had several can lights put in, new fixtures installed including chandeliers, new electrical boxes installed and ceiling exhaust fans upgraded and installed without any issues. Jonathan is very attentive to all details and extremely responsive!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sharon lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ23L84Yc9gIYXaSZLJG-rafWuc472GKJeLYd2sWSBAXo2NNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jonathan, the owner,  immediately contacted me once I submitted my job request. I was very impressed w/his professionalism \u0026 clarifying the job that I wanted completed. His crew did an exceptional job \u0026 I will definitely use this company again for future jobs. In addition, his crew was extremely professional \u0026 courteous. They installed 2 security lights \u0026 ran electricity to my shed. They also installed 2 outlets \u0026 light in the shed. Great job Jonathan.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zach Towler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIZb3jAoi1HvuAqMAJDFn5eGD9wnJ3jb2y1gOwHdpQgF0bkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent work done by John and Savannah! We needed power run to our new stove from the breaker box on the opposite side of the house, John and Savannah made it look easy and left our house looking beautiful. Thank you guys!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
