ctric Contractors! They handled my electrical job with professionalism, efficiency, and attention to detail. Everything was completed on time and to a very high standard. A big thank you to Killian for being especially helpful throughout the entire process—he was knowledgeable, courteous, and made sure everything went smoothly. Highly recommend this company for any electrical work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Salm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT62eU-yUjDrXPht-6R6LapERBxqffZK7zpxEKtQ8yWbX8zHs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Responsiveness, Respect, Integrity\nMy husband Bill and I have hired with Ohio Electric Contractors (Killian Klemencic)  as our electrician for over five years. Their electricians can be trusted to be respectful, clean and courteous, as well as completely capable at their trade. We have used them for very small service calls as well as substantial building and remodeling projects.  Responsible electricians are not going to be cheap, but we have ALWAYS felt that Ohio Electric Contractors delivered an excellent value to my husband and I, and that we have not once been taken advantage of. These are the things that any homeowner should consider – responsiveness, respect, integrity and of course, a can-do attitude, backed up by knowledge and capability.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3l0f0zwgdu_dXrlcykzO628-3HUaibhNEzPFLBNtvwyGimi3jjxc_JSud1rPTiYmabZOLjXXGFjZwDhPOQYM8adnuDCkPKd8vsy_yH3Jt_TJ6hLJ4dixT-BdgpTm7alk9xfgA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2bLZ4yBlDk_pLH5Q4OOgpGlYcxk4L1_fJvIg-RptH2OJDXxXF7VZzJL6rp0IheJ8rCD0-77US0RlHk_MbQiveZuqSQ6_sJ_NuEWOjGQ3sK-j4z2ZuzqQhzZoXkYsaftEOYKKZ7qA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07psXRxLQH2mnXump7PEBNLBdkTfud5ovVeGNnRFXBY51wU625FbSN-GDPKfmI-z7gI-Q7kJ3C1NVHbqK8mLacDHBdinVSEbh-oLV5OEUeiwS8HrxAcUknWxca-TKPRgXKMr9o=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0MfMjnB6GDJAsT