 same day for a fair price. He was friendly, efficient, detailed, and professional.  Before and after photos included. Recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2MmpzJfGCMnWhASkYOtuEENPN8H8zgGrMbsq_dHWJuIxLxwOqhYAs8lT1Q6EhUe7frLfvZJuTIDLHfHO0R0tsyt3jilngZj-RpiY9If_aZF1r82ilrKrARUiyvMTBV_rWKCNhiqRJz_nw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33JYLnwmjiSabXcDbL88ZOGTX4kOj9-HR8TbXcOj3dzZwFSkAdhIRckcba3JFmkocFZStNQ2xC3EpO4J2Vl8tc6PvzKmTt8Zc56eCmVCP24SsRhvc7E6MU32Bov0DNzB2RZmCFGKys4Fs=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-15"},{"Name":"Heather Longman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdXj4jKCIe-hsZYo52Dd2cLzFY-gGbFeglKWfYib0a4SAeT9pStQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time hiring an electrician and I chose this company based on all of the positive reviews about service and cost. I had a great experience with Andres. He replaced my dryer outlet and then did a check of my electrical system. We recently bought the house and the home inspector noted several potential issues. Everything Andres found matched what our home inspector noted. He took the time to explain it all thoroughly, and provided quotes for future work. Overall, happy with the experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Pursel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSgmGaZP6wpRqTO81IrrKQZgHNfh70qfz4tni_b8BzR0qrqJq1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Terrapin. Within minutes of submitting a request for an estimate, they reached out to schedule an appointment.\n\nAsahel did an excellent job understanding my vision for improving my garage. He clearly explained what he could do, along with alternative options and the pros and cons of each, which helped me feel confident in the direction we chose.\n\nOn installation day, Asahel was extremely thorough. He checked in with me about height and placement before starting, and his work was professional, neat, and precise. His knowledge and attention to detail really showed.\n\nI highly recommend Asahel and the team at Terrapin.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenny Leddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb5_AdFC25Q0Gqcig5L_VBmJA6Qx4ct0nfsrJJhYmJKLJU_A5FVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roger came to do a same day install of our ring camera pro which required new 24V wiring  to replace a previous low voltage doorbell. He was quick, kind, professional and asked questions along the way to make sure that the end result was exactly how I was hoping for. Thanks!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0WI-C8nQKSekQhEvpG_2-hhqcbr-jCAXgjT7m4dt2JncbC8KsN_CHLUVOlk1DQJ38KzIRFUA1I66WWQiQfciSQqc4vn6pEMbRFAvmR0CrnabQW9tE2BYFrfMlFA4abnVLi-OiWlqvSpoiu=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-17"},{"Name":"Krista Larsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0VS4nBt9Dkh1BL8RodjfRjLYhW5YxC3WJTNhbfJCmpW3pxFGq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend Terrapin !! Needed an outlet installed in our bathroom and found them on Thumbtack. Scheduling was a breeze- they were able to have a tech come out a couple days later for a quote, which was A LOT better than the other quotes I’d received for this project. The tech Asahel was super great - knowledgeable and SO fast. Great experience overall!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Pelage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhiF_gUdx_ZheUjumyeSVuCJBo4q6BKVPSsMO1k2hHmhU8rcs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Andres  from Terrapin Electric, and the experience was truly exceptional. From start to finish, Andres embodied the highest level of professionalism, technical mastery, and customer-first focus—easily making this the best service experience I've had in years.\nAndres's professionalism is unmatched. He arrived promptly, communicated clearly about the scope of