hed from the base PVC pipe due to ground settlement. But I didn't expect that Austin Energy immediately removed the meter leaving the whole house without power. Tanner was able to come out within an hour of me calling Eskew Electric, provided me a quote quickly and explained in detail how he plan to do the repairs.  Repair was completed in a few hours and Tanner coordinated with the city to put the meter back. I'm super happy the house had power back the same day!. Tanner's work was quick, clean, professional, and great workmanship! I would definitely use Eskew Electric again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5WcNKlXi98AS3AMfby_IXNUMA1hWqrIHFV4sw8bulUbHdvqM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tanner was outstanding from start to finish. Professional, knowledgeable, and easy to communicate with. He showed up on time, explained everything clearly, and did clean, high-quality work without trying to upsell or cut corners. You can tell he takes pride in his craft. If you need an electrician you can actually trust, Tanner is the guy. Highly recommend Eskew Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Mileham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcWxmWTN160bPMg114WYYwq8DsYR85919sC_iTnSvjULwLkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Eskew team has been fantastic to work with and very communicative. We had to move around our appointment a few times due to personal events and the team was super willing to work with our schedule. We had Alden for both our projects and he is great! Super friendly and timely. Had the new outlet and breaker installed in the same time frame as quoted. Will definitely reach out again for additional projects!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bobverdin bobverdin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL88AOyeeRLNcQ5wpPeXAdvLnTz-Tp-dVeJZzwsNQoXle4zWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tanner and his team are the best.  Alden showed up on time, was quick and efficient and professional and did a great job with my exterior lighting needs.  Would not call anyone else if I ever need professional electric work done.  Best in the business!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nico Janssen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuxasSQUWj41umrmHHAcg80jHynxmxVl9oGXs9vHImzE51Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Damien and Marcus with Eskew Electric have helped us out twice now. The first job was adding a 240V line for our new induction oven and the second time was for hanging a Shiner neon sign.\n\nA third time Eskew also fixed one of our electrical outlets.\n\nGreat job all three times!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3iN6v0evNg-rjeAbHW7DHMrOZDzzt4zx4iuETZa5qjeQznu0Rul5iK2wc1i0hw8718SlM4jxkkTTWCLLqjIYBxeFNnkif0Z88vxyCxlzUGLDZnyv8P65NY8iykfLX9eYeYHETppNhXFDuT=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-28"},{"Name":"Rohit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLa9eRfQtXdlx0C_r-T4XlbaK9s1_wPAAZXHsNsyMJAzfvBuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tanner and Damien were great to work with! They were very responsive, professional, and got the job done efficiently. They took the time to make sure everything was working properly once the power was back on and were patient while waiting for the electric company to reinstall the meter. I really appreciated their positive attitude and attention to detail. Highly recommend them for any electrical work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNc--ZlDy5VTDpZJEJbwYSBZ5M0ucn2V5XJMEn9zfKOaZmk3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience with Eskew Electric who diagnosed and replaced 3 worn out GFI outlets in the kitchen and bathroom, so my chef wife can get back to cooking her gourmet meals. Jdi master Jerry and his  Padawan Tanner also diagno