hiqT6DHFPJzVO27Ajxvl=w397-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=JUFLHaUJLCP9qWlkwKcK1w\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=186.37074\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"108848499901589620558","name":"Duhon Electric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108848499901589620558"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Allandale","street":"2121 Shoalmont Dr","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78756","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Vagheesh Narasimhan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyvERGnb8dXQbtsxm6g2KOffemz9_2sN_iGZT1reL5i241uAJ8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Duhon electric is a family run business and they have been amazing and super professional. I had a complex set of needs: including a whole home rewire, a service upgrade, EV charger addition and a bunch of other random electrical tasks. They came over and gave me an honest estimate and then worked rapidly to get everything setup - all amidst coordinating with the city to ensure power was cutoff and then installed. I was very impressed when the power was turned on and everything they installed worked like a charm. Thank you William and Damian!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Ponder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuaWJ98F2hbn56wF8_OetnxMgy51EBTlUgjs72h_gzOqOwQw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend Will Duhon enough. He told me that he is no drama, and man was he right. Other contractors like Fox Services gave me an estimate of $3-$4k for repairs to my main breaker box, but Will explained to me how he could do it for $1k. He did it quickly and with no hassle. It is so rare to find an honest and affordable electrician. But Will is not your average electrician, he is the best of the best in my opinion.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"russell austin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKR_1VCsrhp4boWQWuUAuvLHOE3KrkKDnrSs1127EuL8J1sNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"William has always been very helpful, even initially help me trouble-shoot an issue over the phone. Great communication, responsive to questions and overall very professional. Would definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ana Boza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQbgehfevqMzo-8bQ7Hnqg9fXd3-cb0AfAH-0nH7ovVujLa_xH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We called Duhon Electric about a busted light fixture and were so happy with the service! Prompt, polite, and effective -- they were able to quickly diagnose and fix the problem. We'll definitely be repeat customers for our electric needs and would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Siiteri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ-rISx6oS1WuCbWoiemZAuAaQ2o45sNCYI4zZOMHn6mZG2wv3ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have used William Duhon for five years when we needed an electrician. Today he arrived early and took care of multiple issues - one in the camper 12V wiring and changed out old sockets in our home. Very professional and reliable. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alfredo Silva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFWqj_WOEmYnu2O_YBf6lojAHj9NmnpORzLxc9OWQpnElAV-jD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Duhon Electric.\n\nMy dryer stopped producing heat one night. I called them in the morning and they told me they could be at my home in a few hours! I did not expect same day service, so that was amazing in itself.\n\nThey came out and inspected the dryer (even fixed a wiring configuration on the dryer) and it turned out it was an issue with the outlet. They ran out to get the part and had it up and running very quickly.\n\nI very much appreciated their sense of urgency in taking care of my issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Geoff Dickerson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8JNtZlhGj7CxY90rwkSENx1R5iHJChLQwF3hIFwAC1NIJrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have used Duhon for two different projects and will continue to us them for all of our electrical needs.  They are a great company to work with and are very professional.  William and Damien take the time to explain all of your options, and if they are suggesting something that is needed, why it is needed.  It is very refreshing to deal with true professionals and not some guy with a truck that you find on Craigslist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimba Desai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9cE7FTfe_RPiFSfyeQecqGQ7a0y_T3KoPSPGuxey0g5NY-I5P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was absolutely amazed with Duhon! I was expecting to wait forever, and pay a fortune to have my \"problem\" fixed. William picked up the phone, was friendly and even tried to help me troubleshoot it myself over the phone; who does this anymore?! Amazing! When we couldn't figure it out, he said that he could come out and help me the same afternoon. Again, who does this?! And for such a reasonable price. . . Duhon does! Out of this world amazing service and super friendly. Will be doing business again with him in the near future and he will now be my go to for all electrical work! Thanks Duhon!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
