reet View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=t_ruvfWlC3AE3Mn8EZDK_Q\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=119.40367\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"105428182992546260383","name":"Molitor Electric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105428182992546260383"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Westwood Park","street":"915 Beaver Trail B","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78746","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Theresa Barrios","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJOZTLis835SwR_qPWhQW1tVqaSy_qcl8GgRVR-dFqppdVWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service overall! If I could give 10 stars I would.  We had 4 light fixtures, they came in and replaced all 4 quick and easy.  Very professional and reasonably priced.  I highly recommend Molitor Electric","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Ellen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYQe5_-IgYYEiQooeAUqze32mP6rdyjJfqvA8ZKFx8TSnMC5U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan is excellent to work with. He is the kind of guy you want working on your electrical. He will either do it correctly or he will not do it at all. Which is exactly what you want if you don’t want your house to burn down.\n\nAfter having some seriously substandard work done that could well have burned our house down. I called Dan. I would not have let anyone else do it. I knew he would find the problem and fix it correctly and then I would never have to worry about it again. Which is exactly what happened.\n\nIf you want your electrical work done to the absolute highest standards and within code, Dan is the one to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marco Patino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKTUjjOEtbrzMigEyq2zzR059qN0KJHAvr6xdc5sGRDYcs9jQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Molitor was great! They were responsive, flexible, and professional. Joe was super quick on the electrical work and after he was done, you’d think the new outlets had always been there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tim Lance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAMopD1hun0NxXXejMJ7jfQhiGkCrblT0cdAzJXd33FxwKGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan has pulled my bacon out of the fire more than once over these many years. Super responsive when needed. Quality work always. It is very comforting to know he is there when needed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjab2Tt5b5yM_fP-3irCXT4aGbcefV9VxwNX1cEIKxo-iPLwUI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Since purchasing my home earlier this year, I’ve needed a variety of services performed, ranging from plumbing work to electrical. As anyone who’s owned a home before knows, finding a good servicing company isn’t always easy and can sometimes take a few trials and tribulations. Sometimes though you get lucky and you stumble across a gem right off the bat. In my case, the gem was Molitor Electric. So far, Dan with Molitor has upgraded both house electrical panels, installed a few standard electrical outlets and even ran the wiring and installed two high powered outlets for two vehicle charging stations. At one point during his installation of the electrical panels I asked about the durability and quality of the panels with regards to overall cost. Dan responded by saying that he only used the best of the best for his customers and even though it might mean a high upfront cost, at the end of the install I would have the best panels on the market. As someone who grew up with a father who ran his own construction business for over 20 years, with the ideology of perfection and quality of work, this mentality holds a lot of deep meaning and value to me. Dan’s work is immaculate, detailed and professional. In the case of using an electrician, what you pay for is what you get. If you want professional, quality work don’t waste your time trying different electricians. Just use Molitor.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2bAp5K8nAoXhlPiEKYEd2h0YbB6jBhw_G89wE4Wy15aEZ51lseAE1aNrwKcej-q0KCVQWnHXTqD_WvwM1ytctKe_h83YUAWxT8FPxVowNFxTCWTeafRIi6lE09gc7yUgD4j55L=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yTPryzt-nColl76JMWWeZ0Ixa0wqLZPN_vnM0qjdA-SEqZ102xQAu0Qqc5AYyVvZFtNouPXKYhjRPLdrgmA5wDZtz_iC00H-smAZCLc2imEwyKcG783c4mOsXN-TMhZYqSO_PPw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eBjb7LUKKfWn9qhBK7MkTCc33xIR6fdA5kcjPPA7btXctx_7ozG6AXVDM6gKSe1WLjR3VbiyhE_5Tg7VlqMV4JdZlRZ_iY-aBckTE7U79pLcKIqNiz1aJlbSGb_l755Siz5q8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QCatYLbftBd4jGQBbX7lEv7CvNtdeTkaPKwQcM4DPTTj3tJb_F2JOfoN376ScrYWLfJRcyOHW09s5qopJ0mPVghoQga8FqBxcVmm2Ugawzpvr84q3Q2CedQalKgBfmjJhV6d41w=k-no"],"When":"2020-10-15"},{"Name":"Stephen Donnelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKhDiOdaQT-R4kJD_W2b9RUXvhFhTYJz4VZEBlR8WX4wnLKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan, with Molitor Electric, did the cleanest electrical work I have ever experienced. And my experience is pretty vast. I owned a remodeling company in San Francisco for twenty-five years. We had a microwave/hood that had lost power. Dan diagnosed the problem within ten minutes. Added a cut-in box above the light switch that had fed the micro and re-fed the microwave, exterior light, and plug. NO Drywall or Paint were required. Look if there had been, he still would have been five star. His expertise saved me a couple of hundred dollars in patch and paint. Great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Stout","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUormO8uX2aciU3REsO7QlCcQay6wjMQqy5MXzWCz3UN16RVb-7dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed to have two outlets disconnected and moved before new countertops were installed, and Dan was able to come out the same day. He completed the work quickly, did an excellent job, and was very professional and friendly. Great service and such a pleasure to work with—highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beau LeBoeuf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa2xK5PXlKa5JXeqxkf4BnQtXzTOrkSxukCE4o1oAi_JTHVSgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Joe was prompt, kind, efficient, and very knowledgable.  Molitor is the best when you need an electrical job done quickly and the right way!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
