c so everything was cleanly installed.  They did an amazing job for us \u0026 we are very grateful. Zach explained everything he installed so we understood it - very helpful. He even helped us with the Tesla app to add the charger to it. The price was fair for all the work they did too. I will highly recommend Grayzer to all my friends!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FKSd5iLHpsLOuCQMYWiTt8jGJOwF-ypz_qHtxLDBaL8_huTvO9dQLkoAudVI1jrTdkO5o3VgY6k8QqceFxuIVPxoviAewZ75qdQSSicQasZJK_KAp0v_UBATWmG0ewz_8ew1Dkof0qxc=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0eiVkWbfOl8WJlPor3H-QWt3ekfHNCvhys0MACTpt7KZuJamb1rL-YDrB5utgoEgUZs0RHsp8gr6PPPm3AD7MgBAdUo6VPuFfdZ6IoulE_Wvc9zMwwI4IveKobQkwMERq1R_vFcN8JN6tY=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-19"},{"Name":"Jaswant Ganesan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqPjqU4SlyxhqxVcTlWqjoK_LqEJbnWocHDd9fk8vrufOYuEZK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience with Grayzer Electric when getting my Tesla Wall Connector installed. Their entire quote process was online, which made things super easy. After I uploaded all the required info, I got a quote really quickly. Once I agreed, they sent over a contract for me to sign, and they were incredibly patient in explaining every step of the process.\n\nAfter signing, they gave me a call to schedule the appointment. On the day of installation, they provided an arrival window between 8 and 10 in the morning and even gave me a heads-up an hour before, letting me know they’d arrive at 8:30. Right on time, they showed up at 8:30 sharp.\n\nThe installation team was fast, professional, and very efficient. They explained everything clearly, and even cleaned up the drilling dust by vacuuming the area afterward. They helped me set up the app, made sure the charger was working perfectly, and walked me through the warranty process.\n\nFrom start to finish, the experience was seamless. Top-notch service and great attention to detail. Highly recommend Grayzer Electric!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qX0NI6h1YlMKC1AkHDiV8LtmPsYKJkbUCe4NlmZjMKOMDT-i--XwvwwXTnoKnhc2LgoPtND6WPkTzFm88KPS0R9DnqlHJB-iIjZmrYC4M-eOCAd-VT7mXkHUUkiw21xkZ0apWAc0AWfqu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0QZ6sU1JxWD4bSX6xUQOuCCDDkBcw1BX49byOerZrcQcJ6vDWjtgqdcfdBPTJyCnrGPdGWVophtczrfcW3kSH4twYJqjjmZFs1wwSq4NS1RABe9yVfsjHE0O69QXfmUW007l3hQ50voVNh=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-14"},{"Name":"Ian Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4Fyj5svPf-Ea6XXWkgShkhmFKzlLrSFPItdMe0BiEBTTl5_kK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grayzer was excellent to work with for my Tesla wall connector installation. They provided a thorough and detailed quote and responded very quickly. Their pricing was also very fair.\n\nZack and Todd are awesome. They showed up on time and walked me through the install. They estimated 1.5 hours and were spot on. They even went above and beyond and notified me of a minor issue from a less-than-perfect job that some previous electricians did and took care of it. Love to see that attention to detail and someone who appreciates good quality work. They even cleaned up after some minor drywall work and left the place spotless.\n\nAfterwards Zack walked me through the finished install and helped me get set up with the app. I'm really happy to have worked with these guys. They are very professional, do high quality work and extremely efficient.\n\nThanks for the excellent job. I hope to get to work with y'all again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIIwE_LeHSSBwHDfnKVoZdCrJibU01PWRj1BLpIxs3LggIpBH38Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just wanted to take a moment to say how fantastic my experience with Grayzer Electric has been. I purchased my first Electric Vehicle at the beginning of Aug 23, that same week I started looking for a company to install my home EVSE (Charging device). I shopped around and read lot of reviews and I kept seeing Grayzer come up on Yelp, Google and Reddit. I figured I would get a quote from them for the work and it was magic from there! Their quoting process is simple and easy, answer some questions, upload some photos of your home and they got me a quote within 2 hours that was reasonable. From there, I confirmed the quote and they set me up for installation. They came to my home the next week, they arrived on schedule, were courteous and upfront. Both of the gentlemen that arrived took excellent care of my home and did a wonderfully clean and FAST installation of my EVSE. They even walked me through setting up my EVSE with the app! If you live in the Austin Metro area and need an EVSE or other electrical work done. I would absolutely recommend Grayzer!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-j8kv2iomCI4T00kUyOW9rTGSOhRKCEz2u3lwyq_fgghIizTVDB3zQuNm8Nd3-fTp1kLNTfwHUa3l91sj5hAJgY7OxQoYpuwdpmOsgTfbRF9xfdRP19QnIGT2GuqFsFhN2UD2Og=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2hPpCmdRTHYWJI9v7fObazCY7AJF2lWiJVVjVnX_ujhKYmZwXDu2dxNh8nCFRAlytAXZkRwztuVCUNGz-_QUIuBG59476l53WL8MtcUk3sakDMD7aKWepvRjiLTi-FE0AU4pW7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn29IBSX2r6wDOj2IYaKvv6ZZuqLzQ1zXHhHg81Oj3svy10boXi-6BJLbtignCqej5K9OTNyqxSRbdGT6x3iRtxM_hBKDiQMYrAihWyq6YhAAD1pzn1rT-_IHCULCA7l54lkiLtkkQ=k-no"],"When":"2023-9-7"},{"Name":"Tong Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUohtF-n2AUIEZpOjb6odxsaTXq4xD31SfagULFJ_sxsCY1Rvk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Max from Grayzer Electric, and I couldn’t be more satisfied. He replaced an outlet for my new stove and conducted a very thorough inspection of my entire home’s electrical system. Since the work was charged by the hour, Max worked intensively and efficiently throughout the entire job.\n\nWhat impressed me most was not only his technical skill but also his thoughtful advice on the issues he identified. I asked many questions to better understand my home’s electrical system, and Max was a wonderful instructor — extremely patient and able to explain complex electrical topics in simple, easy-to-understand language for someone without technical knowledge.\n\nHe also went above and beyond to meet my requests. Despite the extreme heat, Max climbed into the attic twice to check wiring connections — even when it was my oversight that required the second trip. Over the course of 5 hours, he delivered excellent work at a very reasonable price.\n\nI’m so glad I finally found the right electrician to take care of my home’s electrical needs. I highly recommend Max and Grayzer Electric to anyone looking for professional, reliable, and customer-focused electrical service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Childs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdhaL3wm1RFhPUPBJdvIxOwj51wI6e0WdKp5KHToTarm4fGQi9wQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Grayzer upgraded my service and replaced my dangerous Federal Pacific panels. However when they encountered non-standard spacing in the wall, they didn't consult with us on how to deal with it and chose the worst possible solution.  They could have reframed the wall section - it's not load bearing - or they could have surface mounted it to the left so I could have put my shelves back up. Instead they surface mounted it so that I've lost use of 25% of my pantry. Completely unnecessary.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catherine Norcom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB7t6DY1u6qfgSjnl4MeS2rynKfL1qZvHx2tDgc3RTn5e3mJp8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I used Grayzer electric for an electric vehicle charging station installation job on advice from two neighbors. They had an easy-to-use online form and were able to fit me in within a day of me emailing them rudder my charging station had arrived and I was ready for installation.\n\nThe installer was professional and knowledgeable - plus, he cleaned up after himself! The install looked great. Pricing was upfront, there were no hidden fees, and I received a very helpful email about claiming tax and electric company credits. I would definitely recommend them!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-3ZM3zG9XbgDC2xXq5jkJf4zeQ4OYfOyJhRKtQNc17yYJIdcvsCjHI1qkzIL47wM3mhFAu4C_uIn8lAm-d2YvaHpZjimWdmLZQVXvn0x-gfZ-nBY83ZlU8zczu7-MggPTSrwQ2w=k-no"],"When":"2021-6-10"},{"Name":"Robert S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVEUWhx3z83ioJKGsyes7neO_7hvhQAynAU_JtrXcacvI_uQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great company had my EV charger installed by Zach who was professional and did the job in 2 hours was really impressed.\nThe quote was so easy. Uploaded pics on there website and the quote came over which was a good price. Booked the job with ease. Thanks Again.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
