erything was up to current code.\n\nHe finished the job, cleaned up everything, and when he left, you wouldn't know a major electrical job had taken place. If you need electrical work, I recommend Jonathan. He’s professional, fair on pricing, and he knows his stuff. Best of all, he’s honest, which is hard to find!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K. W. B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIngptJ5av-BybQUpPl7RYke0Hs7HQvGYzZgmornQWppgXCOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Falco Electrical was very prompt, professional, and accommodating! Able to work around my mom’s schedule and delivered quality work. We will definitely use the service again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Foster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrzI4C-ajbf7NP836mZlv7Rg65pOFzoNYhQdS0uc4AYkoWmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John was great. He arrived on time and took care of everything I needed done around the house. Price was very reasonable.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
