ull,"When":""},{"Name":"Veronica Valladolid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIn1p3AjDkr5J-bA0Q1q-vkoYWY4n9HDBI31dMOC-RfKDvi6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an EV charging system installed and was very happy with AC electric. They were very professional and helpful. Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Bunker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrGSXTB_4ZdoalHM3J0XxFawPpQLBwGYoPDPSoMa4miisLO7G6Qw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an urgent need to get some cubicles hooked up at our Austin office, and AC Electric responded immediately and got us up and running. The charges were exactly as agreed, and the team that completed the work was professional and left the area clean. We’ve since decided to expand our relationship with AC Electric to include commercial work. Thanks, AC Electric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Loebig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCzIg4zT7RaAptbq7Axf7hepIvPxJzlLrVTosSfQnkhT7Sxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AC ELECTRIC Fast,  efficient, expert electricians, very knowledgeable, reasonable costs and great customer service and individual customer relations.\nHave used them several times. Including running power lines and installing a complete structure with 110 and 240 volt service as well as exterior yard outlets. Excellent at trouble shooting problems.\nVery satisfied!\nGary L","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abigail Diltz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQqdDxSklRXbIUceBFvEBUd443WvPzAyA5Kqk1m7YHdqzDUclF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had to give 5 stars as this company answered my call today, sent 2 electricians out to diagnose and price a repair for us after our home buyers were asking for $$$$ for an electrical repair right before our option period ended. In the end, their fast diagnosis, competitive pricing, and quick estimate generation saved us $800 in our concessions to the buyer. Thank you, AC Electric! We will recommend you to all of our Austin friends!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doug Lyon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlkD8hDuzR5cLv0PRSFEvMfrqHZMr3TK40Km_n_-2LguQ43Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible. Not sure the guys who came out were even certified electricians. They came to fix two patio fans that weren’t working. After calling the fan company and getting new internal parts and replacing them they still didn’t work. They finally realized it was the wall switch that was out. They attempted to fix that and whatever they did to the internal parts of the fan really messed them up and they stopped working again.\n\nThen, knowing they messed up, stopped returning our messages.\n\nA real electrician who just came out said wires weren’t connected properly. Do not hire this company.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
