new light switch and mixed up some wires.  He was very nice showing me what I did wrong and how to avoid issues in the future.  I will gladly use CP Electrical in the future with any work or repairs that I need.  Thanks Ram!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGwQI5-N7DX4M2qPW9OW8f0L7RAgZxTDzxarpinW6AcwGrLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ramiro and his team are the best. CP Electrical Contractors have completed numerous complicated projects at my house and their work is impeccable. Ramiro is smart, kind, hardworking and honest (unlike a lot of contractors!) and a breath of fresh air in this industry. His whole team is truly a pleasure to work with and I can’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Johnny Oliden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRqiYFu9Zr_D-gJYc0jZ7w2XzfDSIjwymy7J0Pbp30N1EV6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ramiro and his crew have been doing work for us around the shop for over 2 years now and no job has been too small or big for the company. They have installed all kinds of breaker boxes, step ups, kiln ovens, emergency lights, and over head lighting. They have always been available to start a job within a day or so after the initial quote and have even worked on the weekends to get it done. I would recommend CP Electric to any business or friend with any electrical needs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yGCeEBfPu2FkaLQxAH-vQyB_vw6_6Ga3du7b67pCT0vjg21SY1N1wLfdgEWHJ8BviQHWZR-iDSzNRaQOAf-7zECfowFB6Wpcok-qEDUCT2vqJGry_lRXTXojeLjW_xku6_GNx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3t5L8aXEZ-V7NxAU4Prs1qm3QiIQuvwwOSBB2pn7ckHQ7LYOLt5ddIWK-r4v8nKIIhocKD5gBiLkmO8G_Yu71To2PW0WlRv8gbrj4V88xL_M79QgkorXZhniOLEHew07i7h-Prrw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ncq8plS4vWM03tQrFgtSz_fDfL0aR-fTLZVTWHppwkngn2rYk9xoUZvvneJAZnN1aDo5x2JhnEIAT36nl6vT3x2Nh4-QhnSrEZiR-XB8D-ampKI84VqvV7QjYy7tyT5E191tj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cV0LOQZ0ikmSYDKZIkRFS597DdSS0ehVAXAK4pNy9gHFygwGGpkk6r-R4vaSoxHHz64w0uAhp7_AxnOPL8BWe4EJsWYUsmKJx5MNeTFu3gIidELoWqgkVpsIFl3FhGXsQ0d2-ng=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14iNxxbunEVXaceznWfDkPGwnPRL7x3VeyCjniCF6FUPNKO6f_UYWbZxIbWTk82RG6oK2TzQW0cPHf1I4d8oyY-jG36QLUkoBSS1V_n-W6A6-QwxoXYSjBsCzZ9r_mp9HaFoQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2sy-4Wb4YneUQFOfxlvI3eNKnQETWQDNtLkP_s0M-qGwM6E8NhR5ORNb8NTDDtHba5ZbDRdP0I10RBGc1DUCN8UdldEU_oOwvnHHN8uk4afLR-fWVHBwg6PinfjEPvLzULXTaB5g=k-no"],"When":"2022-3-7"},{"Name":"Maria Camila Betancur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIMw7tO2D-2cThHRVI4iQGbvwYuLiPqAOubfbHWH28hPbKxSd5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the pleasure of working with CP Electrical Contractors and they are absolutely incredible. The owner is very friendly and kind , and really cares about the work. They came through for us during a challenging time and handled all our electrical needs with professionalism, skill, and care. Every detail was done thoughtfully, efficiently, and safely. Their team went above and beyond to ensure everything was completed to the highest standard. We are so grateful for their expertise and dedication and would highly recommend them to anyone in need of reliable, top-notch electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RubyBellaVita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU13Bopi8KAsDlDzpI_ftDqXc2qInWbLHn4o6rUoqPJm5xxY5yZrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We contacted CP electric at the start of the week and by the weekend the chandelier was already installed. Ramiro and his team are extremely professional, clean, efficient, and knowledgeable. We are very pleased with the job.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn06iUj3Cy1MV4eG5cZfsHrE5PpyCrJG1SF0UlphuuG-L2sYbaAZxksiCCV--wtjGoKEW4IvMobC4S00auEs3JfrIpNFUlAQwrNPr6iqaYKF4l9MyxRh20ZkYivsy-nANwM5DouGVA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qCXm-mvpx6lj6ikZEScRGHBkWvl0NeoYi4xXSoz8WYbzOSJJOvSVAfRYOTZucpjN5nkl_SHFAVkiEEfROOqM6T0SbwgBxpPb08jwc4fwN5C-38tyia08AKGM7bcwZ1SC0v7J5=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-11"},{"Name":"David Gross","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIh0QrTCptIFtFA73mtWK8ydzZHHP5wj791ms8i3k6rGe5UbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"CP Electric hands down are the best electricians I have ever dealt with! I have worked with hundreds of different electricians in the past and NONE of them have ever come close to the level of professionalism and skill that CP and crew have.\nI hired CP it install a 100A subpanel in my home garage/shop, along with 3- 220v outlets for my welder/lift/and compressor, and 3- 110v outlets in the ceiling for fans and speakers. They took the time to get everything installed super clean without ripping out my new drywall causing me more work.  I’ve never had an electrician take the time to do such a clean job.  I also had them wire up some outlets in my front yard for our Halloween and Christmas decorations, AND another 50A circuit for my future hot tub.  Again their work was fast clean and EXACTLY what I asked for.\nLastly I had them wire 8 cat6 network drops to my eves for my IP camera system. Again they were meticulous and took the time to get everything wired super clean without causing me any patch work after the fact.\nI know I’ve repeated this a few times but most people don’t realize how important this is to a homeowner like myself.  Nobody wants to have to do more work than necessary, and most electricians I’ve dealt with just want to get in and out and will cut your drywall open to get the job done quickly. Not having to patch texture and paint drywall is a HUGE time and money savings for me, AND my wife is so happy to have a job actually complete off my honey-do list.\nI was recommended CP by one of my neighbor