 undoubtedly result in success. Last summer I put out a bid for my company, needing commercial electrical expertise... No surprise, Michael came out and provide a clear concise estimate of the work. I was unable to be there while the Power Means crew completed the work, confident in their workmanship and abilities to execute. when I returned, every expectation/aspect of the job was met and then some. Better yet, there were no surprises in the invoicing.  Highly recommend Power Means Electrical Services for any and all commercial and residential projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimi Fritsch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITqciEZtTGZXbcBKhHSpyNcy8nUQPPHyMWhmiQfO6WDF-h4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came home from dinner to flickering lights in our kitchen. Spoke with one of the owners KC and they were able to get someone out same day. There was some work the previous owners did that needed to be corrected and Clint was able to fix it and rework the placement to allow for more storage space for us under the sink. First time working with them and will again in the future! Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Archambeault","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXViyKIKQod3BqA1hp638DEpnoxDNZ7_PLkiw1onTF9Yr0SkE1c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need an electrician, call PowerMeans Electric and ask for Clint! He was amazing. Not only did he do great work, but he also made sure to clean up every area he worked in, leaving my home spotless. It’s hard to find that level of service these days. I will absolutely use them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Charbonnet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNmMcq5IXguAvJ0UFCixukL35mfm2Mr1EFRAGgg7bIyclR8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys are the best. Owner really cares and has done multiple times to make sure things are working correctly. Clint has also been over multiple times to help on different issues and has been amazing. Top notch group!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dusty Drake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUC3t3yt20xo-th0Peyy06IBcfwBrphnA3p-l84gbNZBDLEd9lo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve referred PowerMeans Electric to a number of customers of ours at Dynamo Dusty’s Tree Service, and every single one has come back raving about the job. They’re the kind of trades-team you actually enjoy sending your clients to — personable, responsive, and genuinely quality-driven.\n\nWhether it’s an urgent electrical need, a big upgrade, or something the customer just wants done right the first time — PowerMeans shows up, delivers, and your folks are happy. If you want a trusted electrician who plays well with your business ecosystem (and won’t give you headaches later), hit up PowerMeans Electric without hesitation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amelia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0VQar6cfqpEHpk9eGuMx2WCr00195LUykh1tXxYWd0R-4z6U8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After calling many so called 24/7 electric companies after hours to handle a potentially very unsafe situation that required shutting the main off, Mike answered, understood the potential concerns and was able to get swift service to our home after hours with a highly experienced electrician. Clint got us almost fully up and running for the night and followed with a second visit first thing in the morning with the additional breakers that were needing to be acquired during business hours. Excellent, friendly, knowledgeable service and they actually will take care of you after hours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morna Erwin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXzknEFkGOXQnt-8Z9vwxB0Hnnm188D4yMMr4v8eYlX8YAKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One evening we experienced our lights and television flickering and