, and he will always be our go-to  person in Austin!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKY28RGncfetsnjexV29B1LCgfuMgBSSyQnTt3HUnfUYUi2dA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called up Thomas on Saturday of Thanksgiving weekend and he was able to get to my house and fix a sparking kitchen outlet all within 3 hours of the call. Price seemed fair. I would use him again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darrel Simon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzj6QhPBbMvnxLfAyRGSrRCmUzszFnLVsuZwk30SDeb--fzA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thomas showed up quickly after hours and resolved our issue. He’s knowledgeable and reasonably priced. Would recommend him.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
