 of work and attention to detail is what you need as a Electrician. If you watch him as you explain your scope of work to him, you can see him putting together the plan of action as you speek and thinking through the process before he takes actions. He is a great planner which is what I think you need when it comes to electricity.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Torque Nut","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_N-WK0-5yQm7B9CrMIlJHpmTHWuaTmYkekdyk4GaCdpr72Wjf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There are several things in life that should not be overlooked in quality, especially when it comes to your home. For me, Electrical is one of those items. The team at Pritchard Electric took their time to ensure the several electrical jobs I wanted to be completed for my home were done safely and effectively. They all had positive attitudes when on the job, and cleaned up their working area when the job was finished. During the projects, there was an unavoidable scheduling conflict that they worked to remedy by rescheduling and prioritizing the job completion. The team was communicative, courteous, and punctual. I'll absolutely be doing business with them again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caroline Haley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj2qy-m_sjq2kzlM-_3QXJHnNfvc5Wz2jVYtWikLnp3nJFxOpu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pritchard electric did the wiring on my complete house renovation - only things old are the front door and master bath. I cannot say enough about how professional they were and how much i appreciate their attention to detail. Pritchard came back until every aspect of the electrical and lighting were right.\n\nThey made sure i had the right “color” LED in the house and plugs outside for my Christmas lights. Gary and his crew were experienced, thoughtful, and courteous.\n\nAfter the main electrical work was done, i had Pritchard come back to install fixtures etc. They excelled at that work as well even hanging an Apparatus cloud Light where the instructions finish with “pour yourself a strong drink.”\n\nThank you, Pritchard Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Goodman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDlbwOB5pUPVQOv8Fs_5IdPu7vUgObEzKtCiZ0YeLjSCoUfQEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm very grateful that he helped me fix my issue over the phone. A good review is the least I can do to return the favor.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Richardson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz-KnrZgFVeaRJd59t49UPRBIYr3-M8SN5a3wduZUpnUQ3zQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gary and his team are always a pleasure to work with and the work is always professional.  This time was to install an outlet in the bottom of a retrofit structured wiring panel.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMoEtW5Q6Bf62GPn347N6GRzknwqW7jGkBZ7hVCdB98J4oKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service. I highly recommend using this service for electrical issues!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
