een acting weird flashing on and off. A electrician from Austin Energy said there was corrosion in our meter can. Today Ray came out and waited for another Austin Energy to shot off the power so Ray of Bowne could replace the bad parts. He is now waiting for the power to be restore. We are delighted with how Bowne responded so quickly and for the excellent work they continue to do for us.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1oZ3hoZtlwoKDl1VVUzl9mzG8zhe8MrZlj35zykr4zQZ2qU-_4FcwAWLChL3PM8cZeNHykzlC1DLcX0LTldD81YxMpgWkOU0AL3JOTama9ExA-BShXqcQBuItfuVJIe4DYv_iZEQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jpJmpicVbCU3_m5leycglcPXzWc4ZTpyka-ClR0wzBYsZAT8nMp3WwNo9DWXZhd19K7xjFn7olLQJYpCnnwEIp1NwHP6NAyiEy1Rk8_3oj--PgWTbDnjnr-JcyzBE687lqIRF=k-no"],"When":"2023-3-23"},{"Name":"Krystle Blanchard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh7r1Hd5niNDrZhNfdEg_CE_MHAeOLjr25Ic8QfFrHfg3pknUjBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have not used your company but I do believe that the people you have workqing for you represent you. With that being said I watched one of your vehicles leave a bar/restaurant and drive erratically.  Speeding, riding bumpers and on his phone. All in a 45 mph/under construction neighborhood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mina Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDrqdOeDAq6hylksFnAe0jLnpc_6SiD297StIJbDdV1C1YaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired at least three -- maybe four -- electricians since we bought our house four years ago for various issues. Our experience with Bowne has been SO GREAT, relative to any others. Their technicians really know what they are doing, they are excellent problem solvers, they schedule quickly and efficiently and come when they say they will. I was especially impressed with Ray, he is very pleasant and figured out how to wire and hang my exterior speakers which wasn't easy to do. AND they clean up