ill use them every time!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JonJon Bridge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDREYZjzkhVSyNeBBSglDs2TRBCEQ95MVxWFernrUQSkD-FGNR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was hit with a new City of Austin code requirement to get my electrical system inspected and signed off by a State of Texas licensed Master Electrician prior to an upcoming Health and Fire inspection for my small restaurant.\nIt was a challenge to find a Master Electrician who was familiar with this  type of inspection, with a couple saying they could (unconvincingly) do it. I was starting to get stressed until I got a call back from Jeff! In a calm cool collected voice, Jeff said \"Yeah, we can get that taken care of that for you.\" After 1 minute of chatting details, I could tell that Jeff knew exactly what type of inspection I needed, so I immediately scheduled an appointment with him for 2 days later.\nWe met up, he did a quick walk through, opened up my breaker panel, asked me a few questions, examined other areas, and informed me of a couple of items on the City of Austin's inspection checklist where I would fail.  He also told me that he had the needed materials on his truck and he could knock them out and sign off on my inspection sheet. After Jeff told me how much he would charge me for the extra work, I was pleasantly surprised! It was obvious that I was in a tight spot with my big city inspection coming up, but Jeff was very reasonable with his quote!\nLong story short, after completing the work and signing off, I realized that this man was 3 things. Reliable, Reasonable and Professional. I will give out referrals on this man for the rest of my life!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Treva Williamson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJedFSacvuQxze0gjZ6MptipgTDzYka8BWGFYNnAfmvNGnrBH_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Flash Electric has done a lot of work for our church over the past few years. Jeff Harris is super knowledgeable and super nice as well:) He has done just about every type of electrical work for us, from major commercial, all the way down to the little electric pump in the rose garden fountain. In the service world today he is a standout!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Mendez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVW9ybQe0hnkt8cjyyerY7K0tpZOp1GXnwg-X6zwBDIf84gdylKjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeff did such a great job when he came out to fix my electrical issues (breaker \u0026 outlets)! Very professional, helpful, informative and friendly! I'm very lucky to have had the type of experience from him. I definitely recommend him for assistance. Thank you so much for everything and all you do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Williamson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-lUWnrJe7erFlzZKzQQ8YTB5SqrUGRvigf19teMzDGx_m9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have had Flash Electric complete several projects for us. Jeff is truly a Master electrician. All of the work that he has done for us has been of the highest quality. We plan on using Flash Electric for all of our future electrical work. I can definitely recommend him for all electrical projects.\n\nPastor\nCalvary Apostolic Church","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
