.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7cV8vOOOnqHs0FTw6ZwClgS4oXYkkIekYStR-2DgGtoDVqDk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Garrett come out to install new lighting in our kitchen and fix a few switches that didn’t work. He was super knowledgeable and clearly takes pride in his work. He even noticed a potential fire hazard on another circuit and fixed it on the spot. Prices were fair and the service was excellent. I’ve already told a few neighbors about them, definitely keeping them on speed dial for future projects.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn06erP-r6I4mDX0vO2FW9-YkewRmLhfzM5HjNwrl7PD9O-_y3YMIvwE3hUmjpx3LNlpe8qXMmgpeneDLmiNHVT4c9zu5rkCO_cEStw_FqBcg3_S1ZfGSUzrQy5887_9C9df9ry5y3-rQA88=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3QzfMjNhCd9L0HoNVPldJXbRk3SSI7gAPHDi7GFj3SY97G6p65j3-BDm8ihhAddphQw8VR7guYRARuIY999o6f_sP5JcIOvIUDXoJXzVkfTVo_hYL3c9vwSm_2EpzisGumBcuZhKk6S6kL=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-20"},{"Name":"Mandy McPherson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL6TOO9pIVC_YkfaqoPVck85YFwv2OcKJLqHOzpq-bAv5aKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The scheduling team all the way to Garrett and David with Keil Electric were amazing! I had some companies come out to give me a quote on an older electrical system in the home we just purchased that was looking a bit corroded and in need of some repair. We were experiencing some flickering on interior lights and a fried microwave. They did a great job at being honest and thorough with us offering us three different repair pathways depending on what we could afford and/or wanted to do. They did the work same day and replaced all the interior breakers and the entire panel w/breakers outside as well installed some LED disc lights for me. They did all this in 2.5 ish hours, lighting fast!\n\nI plan to have them back out to install some fans and additional light fixtures once I make my fixture selections.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yIfACKLVj499oY-PKbm3xnlTZW6BFAP6mGtkWcKO-6KWFYR9RKt9M9MAFoZ8isB2DqX1fOv630y2Bt1BA_PG0R27CpcnPg6vdaz4olPXHGxGv_GMh5my9Ul-sHSpvJgryvysVrdUN9Q=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-30"},{"Name":"Veronica Nobles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6jO2rsoN3lp1L7WDsFqTor9nBIXV2aj34Cu3EYlO95p57mxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came across a Keil Electric ad on Facebook at the perfect time.  My lights had been flickering whenever the AC turned on, and despite purchasing a larger hard start kit from the AC company I use, the issue was never resolved. So I scheduled an appointment with Keil Electric and I'm so glad I did. Garrett came out and thoroughly inspected all of my wiring- - from inside the home all the way to the meter loop. I was shocked that the original home inspector had missed so many serious issues. Garrett provided three clear estimate options to bring everything up to safety standards, and I chose the one that best fit my budget, which included redoing the meter loop. The condition of the meter Loop was far worse than I realized: the PVC conduit had never been sealed, rainwater was running down into the underground line, corrosion was setting in, and even wasps nest had formed inside it was ready for a National Geographic movie haha. Garrett also discovered that my breaker box had the wrong size breaker for my AC unit, which could have prevented it from shedding it off safely in an emergency. Thanks to their work, everything was replaced Dash Dash new breaker box, new meter loop, and a new exterior box that the AC was connected to that was badly corroded and exposed to the elements. I decided to test this company with a project to other electricians told me was \"impossible\": installing  track lighting above nine Pantry cabinets in my mobile home.  The other companies claimed it couldn't be done without attic access. Well one member of Garrett's team completed it in under 20 minutes, with all the wiring cleanly running through the ceiling - - and they even included it at no extra charge because they care. Now I can finally see all my cabinets clearly ( even the spider webs!), and it's genuinely inspiring me to get everything organized and clean. I am a happy woman! To top it off, Garrett labeled every breaker in the new panel with very easy to read handwriting. It was all professionally done like my family took care of me. So thank you so much to Garrett, David, William, and Alex I feel safer in my home and I'm truly grateful for the quality of the work and the Integrity this team showed from start to finish and clean up.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn11aFscZEItxKicFhLO1VcOOT7yiReGSWEYV3FJz2VCoBc7YbgOEKykh9KMIjXJVYDlpE6ZwlI6JZbkrg7RafupVCS_IooZQahxklAoh6H9AMhbcmwN4Cj5gj7ERMKOVo544RbtnGKeWtE=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-2"},{"Name":"Josiah Bryant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUs5rQviUgQKKRcb3A52PD-D2KoMwS5KxE7XeEKFs0jIbIRiy4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an outstanding experience with Garrett. They arrived right on time, were extremely professional, and explained every step of the electrical panel repair. I felt confident in their work, and now my panel is safe and up to code. Highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cameron Luck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVNopL_o9mN2OcS2SKnGlVTZsaBN9ZRzObkkT45cCMX4T3sTBF_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Garrett and William quickly came out, gave an estimate, and installed my Tesla wall charger in minutes. Amazing work and honest company. Will definitely work with them again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3SZ37zEnayXEg_GV49ZT6AgrlWAE0ro6OEavGhsObEQzDTYREN-ZGvfqOOqJ_k0DCM96CjjYN6cEMfLB0BEEqJkeIiMXEzhOx5xxw3vmPaUN55ynlF9Eao0w_2TAc3P41t8TQKHDDAn0Q=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-31"},{"Name":"John Bickenbach","ProfilePicture":"https://