UWv4d14hYZpn3oeT_F6fU3KMJvh4V3M3uZG2AhehD8dKpxHhB1q3c59NXbPo1D6ciCaHMzOaT9s4Lks5AzJJDmXFUDgkCFZv4AGQPd=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3slqbQbWXh4ZGrGcCcdLLHulKzoDyu7U3Q8dKWtVNgCnlcgckzvJTCf2Gg85A5Uj-98BfsvgbiEPu4af1GiFl4SUOTZDzw7bOiS8uKVPBSG6bhU_ZXz_8cPYdlyWz-EJmEwoEnDKq4Byo=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-13"},{"Name":"William Fitzpatrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUREbbRWkABu4N20a0sDxCLtEYLVO_jBxf1mOxA8zvB9Miead8-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These are the guys to call for all of your household and commercial electrical needs. We had a partial power failure but resetting breakers did not resolve it.  We called one provider (rhymes with  Mr. Mularkey) who failed to find the issue but still warned us the house “was at risk” due to an “old” main electrical box.  Mularkey wanted to charge thousands and insisted we needed their “Power Club” membership, even threatened to CHARGE MORE if we didn’t join! Johnny and Tom from Cedar Park Electric came to the rescue just two hours later, found the issue and repaired it for less than $400 and without once asking us to join any clubs.  They were friendly, professional and fast.  Avoid the Mularkey and just call Cedar Park Electric when you need help with your power problems!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Paparazzo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE9l7T1ffB20MFOsySJ0sAd5Vd19Nm1DcT0h6AHI_2oEBzcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Cedar Park Electric, and I cannot recommend them highly enough. From start to finish, they were nothing short of exceptional. The team displayed an impressive level of professionalism, reliability, and integrity that immediately put me at ease. It's rare to find a company that combines such honesty and trustworthiness with top-tier expertise, but Cedar Park Electric does exactly that.\n\nThey installed can lighting both inside and outside my home, transforming it into the dream home I've always wanted. The work was done with meticulous attention to detail, and they completed everything in a timely manner, without cutting any corners. Not only were they affordable, but their pricing was also transparent, with no hidden fees or surprises—just straightforward, honest service.\n\nWhat truly stood out to me was their demeanor. The entire team was incredibly well-mannered and respectful, making the entire process smooth and stress-free. They took the time to listen to my ideas and offered their expert advice, ensuring that the final result was even better than I had imagined.\n\nIf you're even considering any electrical work, Cedar Park Electric should be your first and only call. They turned my old home into a place I now absolutely love, and for that, I am deeply grateful. Thank you to the wonderful folks at Cedar Park Electric—you have a customer for life!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robin Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYXDFy2VMo2BbvGENtz_MHMZAlpKDUiDNA_dJ2fGIKlE9Enps=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used Cedar Park Electric several times and have always had a great experience. Recently, the employee that was assigned to our job ended up leaving the company after he finished our lighting but before he finished the drywall. It was difficult communicating with this ex employee but when I contacted Johnny, my project was completed immediately. I really appreciate him and Cedar Park Electric. We will recommend Cedar Park Electric and use them again in the future for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frances Ortiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5yz2Z_dJjJG8C22nR6rsZjgklHijqdIi7Nhi2CYZAib-7Zc7yUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently hired Cedar Park Electric for a complete electrical overhaul in my home, and I couldn’t be more pleased with their service! From start to finish, the entire experience was seamless. The team was punctual, professional, and incredibly knowledgeable. They took the time to explain every step of the process and answered all my questions with patience.\n\nWhat stood out the most was their attention to detail and commitment to safety. They ensured that all the work met the highest standards and even offered helpful advice on energy efficiency. The pricing was fair and transparent, with no hidden costs or surprises.\n\nI highly recommend Cedar Park Electric to anyone in need of electrical services. They exceeded my expectations in every way, and I will definitely be using their services again in the future. Thank you, Cedar Park Electric, for your outstanding work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6NDlb2Eih4XA_37g4zoTS8_VnxwpbjysTFoc-0vXkfecGt_Ki=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fast, efficient, professional, courteous, friendly. I called to have them come out and diagnose/fix a breaker that kept tripping, and to install an outlet in my pantry. After talking it over with Blake, I ended up having him install a whole-house surge protector at the main supply breaker box as well. Blake did everything super-efficiently, and effectively. The price was very reasonable. I'm very happy with the results, and I'll definitely be calling them back if I need electrician services in the future.\n\nWould recommend without hesitation!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Lerner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJ4VX2BEeZI4R-C0FyYrBqiDQEyYmdtVm0l8hWCTqdBsmxPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a tree downed the power line to my house, Johnny and Tom did an excellent job of assessing what work needed to get done, obtaining emergency permits and inspections from the city, making required repairs, and working with the city and Austin Power to restore power to the house. Excellent work!","Images":null,"When":""}]