SUGCxWWucD5MNC-TByLn5m3K=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=buDQkeDeFPLqWswBjonO5A\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=95.9835\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101148945694625082315","name":"Brushy Creek (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101148945694625082315"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Anderson Mill","street":"11613 Star View Trail","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78750","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as veteran-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Ben Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtmsu07m9eZaur5YCl2M9R2YmBEYq8Yhs-xVb5L7cs_3gaAKas=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Greg has been nothing but professional and efficient. Our panel and house was broken which left us without electricity. Our home warranty was not helpful at all and couldn’t find a good contractor to do the work.\nGreg came straight to the rescue. What took 2 weeks of headache was solved within a couple days with Greg.\nIf anyone needs any electrical work done, big or small, Greg is the man.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martin A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5J7ihVxHN9urK2z5bitYwKP6Oa2sstNn8bD_uOjgMvluxmkc2bA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Greg came and installed new breakers on my Eaton panel, simple job but he was professional and easy to communicate. He helped me out when one of the new replacement breakers that I got was used, kind of extra mile from him. Will use it in the future. Definitely recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sri Chakravarthy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2lbtUHDaVk9zBNiuRR3ce3Mxn4AS9ouSYVTtcUTFNVOj5beiH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For replacing an old electrical panel, I called around for quotes. I got quotes in the 4k-6k range. But Greg at Brushy Creek electrical was very reasonable. In addition, Greg was very professional and did a clean job. I will highly recommend Brushy Creek electric co for all electrical work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1zfkK0lIz_Dqzg-YhNa47phLwtMUEb8cnSN9mhkwFt-rI8kXb9urpsGs6ekb07D9kQL76Vd0lcUE1aaxiWRXWYSi01-xcz8tMtFPPxN4RVtANwpivTnBrFUpPuJzlTVCU2QrmYQg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DOmhbcwnH1L0nqQeDGM8j8bZMRuJiJ3ehQxouS6suI8P7Lldxl_y3EEhVa0_d0FOoIXJXAC3QuEvmk2paE0jnr1gpC7qu5IBXuouUhlUoD-A--6XanSRmYdqmw7aJBv6OBiYY=k-no"],"When":"2022-6-18"},{"Name":"TRIMBL3","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXN-6V9AIilmybONllFHtCKQGovJB4nw9wSwzkV6FB61bFE4D0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was looking for electrician services near me and found Brushy Creek Electric. The owner, Greg, was prompt, professional, and knocked out our sauna installation for us like a true veteran electrician should (he's been doing this for 35 years). We had other companies come out and say they couldn't get the job done because it was logistically pretty difficult, but Brushy Creek Electric got it done in a timely manner and it works incredibly well. The wire management he did was also MUCH more discrete than what other electrician companies were suggesting. All of this was done for an incredibly fair price too. I would recommend his electrician services to anyone. I'll definitely be a repeat customer when I need anything done in the future. Thanks again Greg, we love our new sauna!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1DLXP1gDpX-7BVndoomBjgNZ388TSp8oFx_T5Sg9m_rm2vfT4V52lPvLOXh5zrzES1TQxBTIJhcO5wct_j9ydRHId-5w7W8deKaLzmXesMWKzz8Q2RvmMdA5qnyZb82_cRmrymhg=k-no"],"When":"2021-8-22"},{"Name":"Anthony Collier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1cfi2fs6U4XKNC7edZ_FbKHhnIIc8U1HOelfjGwKOarJwkfuT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Holy smokes, Greg was beyond exceptional. Called him in the morning and he came out in the afternoon. He didn't have the breaker we needed so he went and got it and came back on the same day! I expected him to push me to the next day but nope, same day service. There are a lot of unreliable contractors today but Greg is not one of them. Adding to that, super nice guy. Not the fake customer nice, genuine good person nice.  If you need ANYTHING electrical related, Greg is your guy. Storing his number in my phone because he will get all of my business moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGeIdFWcuHhu2e9JUXH4kDwbHdnZdCeOdUeZpBTFLYPrzMKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Brushy Creek Electric. Greg is 100% awesome! We were in a real bind and needed a meter box replacement in the cold weather and after business hours. Greg not only came out but stayed until the job was done at 3 in the morning when it was 14 degrees outside. Not only is Greg a true master but he is dedicated, honest, reliable, and determined to get the job done right. Thanks Greg!!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dwight Vance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIf-c7SgRx-eVvJWqTBZvJkT9Yx2DgSSakrDTx8-r5IqjZigg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a terminal burn out in our meter box.  The electric company came out and found the problem.  We called Greg and he gave us a very reasonable price and said he would be here in 30 minutes even though it was 10 pm and the temperature was 15 degrees and the wind chill -1 degree. He arrived when he said and then waited for 2 hours for the eccentric company to return and shut off the electric.  He and our neighbor, David were out in the weather for over 5 hours.  He fixed the problem and the bill was what he told us even though he had to spend a lot of time waiting. When I need an electrician again I will call Greg.  I would give 10 stars if I could.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Gatten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgnoqvlzlH8JCUha4XsIqeWrNCHt-f-fwKfTqdgifLy1IfsRI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This guy showed up hours late, did not apologize or even explain.  He charged more than other electricians for the same simple job, and the more complex job I had for him, figuring out why my lights flicker and periodically just stop working altogether in some rooms for days at a time with no explanation, he just threw up his hands and said sometimes old houses are just like that.  Turns out I needed a new circuit breaker.\n\nExpensive, bad at his job, and late -- there is no reason to hire this guy.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
