ntastic and they are great people. Any issues we've ever had have been small and they have remedied them immediately. Can't recommend them enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Deems","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOiH-zIVk0JTXXnBPR4AyRtSYKJxsb3oxBQwGmc15nDKOP0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company is unmatched by any other electrical company in Austin.  It's\n\nran by a group of people that have extensive experience in this field and in this city, and in my opinion nothing can compare.\n\nEvery employee at Beckett is highly trained with strict standards to bring you the best, safest, and most professional service you can find because they value your safety and satisfaction above everything else.\n\nWhen you outline a goal they make it happen.  It's that simple.  They consider your budget and make it work for you.\n\nBeckett has retrofitted many high-end professional businesses like Google, Facebook, and Samsung and they continue to do so with pride.  If you can imagine it, Beckett Electrical can build it for you.\n\nIf you're a smaller company and want to make your business look modern and attractive, Beckett will absolutely fulfill your needs and they will help you imagine a plan that works for you.\n\nThis company also treats their employees extremely well and makes sure they are well-educated in the latest electrical theory and safety measures.  They even pay their employees to go through specialized training so they can live to their utmost potential.\n\nBeckett makes sure to take care of those who make all of this happen and that results in happy employees who are dedicated to envisioning a better world through their work. A better world that you can help us build!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Turner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhB1CzSG6q7KuNgsT7LBfn62qcZ32X7B1eUQWmu8r0Gcw1jA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have never used this business, nor would I use it in the future. They are receiving this bad review because of their habit of TAILGATING on the highway. I was going 47 in a 45 mph hour zone and they left a good one inch between us, very unsafe. Then a school zone came up and I slowed down to 30, again, they were riding my bumper and decided to just switch lanes and speed in a school zone. Would NOT recommend this company to anyone if it means putting other drivers at risk for their impatient driving. Recommendation: Put your drivers back in driving school to learn how much distance to leave between you and the car in front of you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelsey Life","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjhZcyuEAKFiHI8GfYuel5Z_YXEgq_4jcK6ys5LBARpdU5wmpx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Barry has been such a pleasure to work with! We manage a community out in Manor, TX and it was having various electrical and lighting issues that nobody was able to fix for quite some time. Barry and the team at Beckett Electrical were able to get out there promptly and get everything up and running again! We now use them for all electrical issues within the community.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Burke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIp5YaZkqn8ry6v05UJAZpfmGK0l6QOlXDZGzFDQtd1gjMnsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ruben and his team were amazing!! Even with the complexity of the job, they stayed in communication with me the whole time. Strongly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
