easy to work with. They treated my home like their own and went above and beyond to deliver a finished product that exceeded expectations.\n\nMy home is now significantly safer and better equipped for the future because of their expertise and dedication. I cannot recommend Brad, Nash, and the StarTech Electric team highly enough. If you want electricians who take pride in doing things the right way, these are the guys to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kay Silver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAwT-upptOrTPoJ9tedOCfJH1owPQWhOPrDxq7D6M7deVYUCmb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've used them for years and have never had less than a fantastic outcome.  Fast, reliable service and really great communication.  Grateful there are still family -owned businesses like this one that are focused on building relationships with their clients!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Rowland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQyk-Oi4bEA0Utl9wihJdRT_psKsVGBYZve3JTwhBxQ7v75nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've worked with Startech twice now, once on a project prepping a home to be sold, and recently again to help address electrical issues in our new home and hang TVs. I can't speak highly enough about how helpful they were both times. Recommended only what was needed, got the job done quickly and were extremely knowledge and courteous. Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Marquess","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-4U4YYQ5HrGrYL3IOTjltHpYFAhsuZOHVHkLEHvblF_-xxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish, StarTech was absolutely perfect!  Everyone from my first call to the two great guys who came out were friendly and helpful.\nPatrick and Brandon were quick and efficient in getting the three problems I was having fixed.  They both were great at explaining what the problems were and how to fix them.  The price