my new go to electrical company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carl Allen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-WGMd-i1EPsIUHZEvxEL-l3xqgJPnFuS2-KaCntYZX2jluA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic service from Startech. From visit to quote to completed job of installing a big EV charger and fixing a light was only 24 hours. Very professional and polite operatives I highly recommend this local business and will not hesitate to use them again. Thank you","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
