rder_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"100049496804870866764","name":"Velectric (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100049496804870866764"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"16400 Rocky Ridge Rd","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78734","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Steven R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXegecFSGGbjJHYncENWbuTbYuVLILC3vlHsZ7S2FzKpMfiK22a6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Velectric was super easy.\n\nAs we've learned the past couple years, the TX power grid and the grid in Lakeway aren't the most reliable. We sought to get a generator inlet and interlocking switch so that we won't be left without power.\n\nAfter getting quotes from 3 companies, Velectric's initial quote was the only one that was within range of my expectations based on my research. Mario allowed me to provide my own inlet and cord to stay within budget. He even gave me a good deal on a whole home surge protector install as part of the visit.\n\nWe were able to schedule within a week. They showed up on time, did the work with minimal down time–they cut the power only for a few minutes, and did a nice, clean install.\n\nEverything worked as expected when I tested it. Now we can run our A/C in the summer or our heat in the winter even if the grid goes down for days. That gives my family peace of mind.\n\nThank you Mario and Junior!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0hGhVuOV0nJUmWvT6mX_nPdz9QzsYIvGYu0dbHAjR6t_RuWn0A6PQKi8zzfEfUCNtaX4L_e6HmGddhTILkd0xbsi6G4gsOxV6UUDaDGEmfiVteXWugNH_CuYV_Gic6IoLsVQnC=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0kOQ6YXPtNei6q9kIpJno-9oZmycQC48fD6l3M4vji33uf5r5jp59WycsJUPv65oFu_VkLNQMU7luk3Wpuwi34ahjQtn13r9G6PVcBf2GErY5vcC1UKSd_Ea0ztSX3l-b_dGgu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0pPkUUIfqwjPG_iF4Fj9eCa9nHVuyJRsi8yYFKJbQPKEYGMWcNHOY8rgVbGh0lP9c6M3MtUhIzCETHOJU2Ib7tK87LxOtaS3gvgnoY78eGnsN75VZ3xYEODSu9SY1N79rFi0ZP=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2LH9LT-FeTL7WESW66XiTjGfiddBz-KcrPPLmRWt93KE28KhiyB9DWEPAkfRanDNEd9pLQTChBcuGs45Vnub0Ujwqab4Dc8By2iTkDomXOKFFOkr4uE4gxWEry3UjyinI6TWhCFA=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Ana Mills","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj5T1iT-gLrlSrqGC5niMXJW9ON_f35jk68FKseEoCEUoiILk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Velectric was a breath of fresh air. I have worked with many electricians and Mario and his team have been by far the most professional. They are quick, clean, thorough and super knowledgeable.\nI’m very grateful to have found them and will continue to use them for all my future projects. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Cirujales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjoz5IVy2Yn6AmcPqtzUCbbjQNK4rj4tBNmTVmzWBpGnL0iiYkgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Velectric was very enjoyable!  They are top notch professionals that were punctual and professional.  Mario had very timely communication, went very in depth in helping troubleshoot my electrical issues, and made sure that I was satisfied with the final product.  I hope I never have any future electrical issues, but if I ever do, I will definitely reach out to the Velectric team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jantzen Slaughter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURFXBJ9l3lDZlPXaVRPh9VWowUXmuTG6HnVf_1D9Kkw7Xn1es=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Velectric provided top-notch service from start to finish. Their team was punctual, professional, and incredibly skilled. They explained everything clearly and completed the work efficiently, leaving the area spotless. Highly recommend for reliable and high-quality electrical work. Truly impressive experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsZgie7Cm3EAYyC6Ht--wRSN7sGsj-Y_UHVxalZ_GzuP_mxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mario responded quickly and had Junior come out and solve my issue within 30 minutes of getting to my house. Got some great peace of mind knowing I didn’t have a fire risk. Thank you fellas.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel and Ashley Eaton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9-PBgbczPZwJkHACOcK1IwLnhloPkAa31-WVfoshGX_I0IrTy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"VElectric helped us troubleshoot and replace two of our bathroom exhaust fans. Mario was great in communicating, upfront about pricing, and arrived on time. He was able to get one of ours fans going without replacing it, which we appreciated, and replaced another as we requested. It wasn’t as straightforward as we thought, so we are glad we hired him to do and didn’t try to do it ourselves. Would definitely recommend VElectric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Chavira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT8MnnKYXW_bbZCCZ999pDvmFDq7htuHHXz42WzFoBQvTelg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"September 2024 update: Very happy returning customer. I’m grateful to have a reliable electrician who I can count on. Thank you, Mario and team!\n\nExcellent work and transparency in the issues we had. I already have Velectric in mind for future jobs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raj Mukherjee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB7FqCsDgL3BwEUVOp9aFF5h26oZcqLx5tDGsH9ndhoKy3Qd9p=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"During Texas winter storm of 2023, we lost power. The problem was a tree branch that fell on the electrical wire. It took down the riser, weather guard etc.\n\nVelectric was incredibly responsible and responsive. Since the time we agreed on a quote (very reasonable price) to the time it 